{"tid":1041460,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「即使」VS「即便」- 可唔可以唔好再搞錯？","createTime":"2019-02-28T23:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T02:27:28.000Z","uid":83025,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"12b915077c21544f8c02845fdfd3a8038a86c287","tid":1041460,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:29:56.000Z","msg":"真係頂唔順啲人再撈亂兩隻字黎用。由幾年前大陸網絡小說興起就見到大量人誤用，明明由細到大都係學<strong>「即使」做假設，「即便」係完全唔同意思</strong>。每次見到啲人用錯都好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTL;DR: <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「即使」是連詞，用以引導一個表示「假設」的從句，以強調與假設之事相應的狀況。</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">例句：有了你，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即使</span></strong>沉睡了也在笑。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">而「即便」可當作副詞或連詞。當副詞時，用來修飾動詞，其意義為「於是立刻就要&hellip;」。</span>[/b]<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">例句：玄德聞布相請，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">即便</span></strong>欲往。（劉備獲知呂布的邀請後，立刻就想赴約。）</span><br />\n<br />\n---------------<br />\n<br />\n近年來，不少人將「即便」當作「即使」來用，大有氾濫成災、一發不可收拾之勢。<br />\n事實上，即便與即使不僅詞意迥異，詞性也大不相同。<br />\n<br />\n「即使」是連詞，用以引導一個表示「假設」的從句，以強調與假設之事相應的狀況。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">例句：有了你，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即使</span></strong>沉睡了也在笑。</span><br />\n而「即便」可當作副詞或連詞。當副詞時，用來修飾動詞，其意義為「於是立刻就要&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n句型上，「即便」用在主句中，之後緊接動詞，其間不得插入名詞性的主語；主語經常會省略，如不省略也只能放在「即便」之前。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">例句：玄德聞布相請，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">即便</span></strong>欲往。（劉備獲知呂布的邀請後，立刻就想赴約。）</span><br />\n<br />\n而當「即便」出現於主、謂語間，則為連詞，位於主語之前；此時與「即使」的分別在於「即便」用在縱予分句之首，從言說者的角度出發，容認一事實，而「即使」則是用於假設分句之首，假設一非實然前提。<br />\n<br />\n再者，「即便」與「即使」的分別還可追溯到「便」與「使」的不同，早在六朝「便」就用為縱予副／連詞，例如：「其勢不分，眾寡莫敵。我便救尾，無以制之。」（《周書．李賢列傳》）<br />\n因此，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「即便」與「即使」根本是兩個不一樣的詞，絕不可以混用啊！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以往，「即便」一詞常見於古文中，在現代口語裡本用得極少，但不知從何時起，開始有人在講話時習慣用「即便」來取代「即使」，甚至連流行歌曲與新聞媒體都依樣畫葫蘆，一再誤用。<br />\n<br />\n希望能藉此番說明，讓大家明白，<strong>即便並不等於即使，就像大便絕不能拿來當作大使</strong>，千萬別再誤用了啊！<br />\n<br />\nCredit: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/bXZYUs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbXZYUs&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=9303f9cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/bXZYUs</a>"},{"pid":"4a26d29bfc84abd50ad157076a2c7020248f60c8","tid":1041460,"uid":2419,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:37:04.000Z","msg":"越黎越多on9仔俾大陸劣質文化影響左都唔知"},{"pid":"7656220919224e38ab72cf1f51886f61394974f2","tid":1041460,"uid":45601,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180129/20288256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180129%2F20288256&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=e95e3bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180129%2F20288256&h=17fa513c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180129/20288256</a><br />\n清未民初都有喎，係咪矯枉過正呀"},{"pid":"a4a1605d53659b6f46a271629c794b9e7637d37d","tid":1041460,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:48:41.000Z","msg":"台灣都係用即便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且用 弄不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6b1844c1cad72d932f67700df6f13895e479ea","tid":1041460,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:49:01.000Z","msg":"智障中國人係咁"},{"pid":"a95e53fe65212ead6a25a1f4d786c39a83f889e3","tid":1041460,"uid":146340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7656220919224e38ab72cf1f51886f61394974f2","tid":1041460,"uid":45601,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180129/20288256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180129%2F20288256&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=e95e3bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180129%2F20288256&h=17fa513c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180129/20288256</a><br />\n清未民初都有喎，係咪矯枉過正呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:53:43.000Z","msg":"佢地開完po屌完就唔使負責任架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3547a5bcaa13598e4f40eb4b390397770c93d3a","tid":1041460,"uid":133877,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"睇返以前嘅漫畫,真係冇見過即便<br />\n奇就奇在得一兩個人咁寫就話姐,而家差唔多個個都寫即便<br />\n即係一班由以往譯/寫即使嘅都變埋做即便?<br />\n究竟係咩事"},{"pid":"16ab00451f5d2772badfb2dada161d2555f591ec","tid":1041460,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7656220919224e38ab72cf1f51886f61394974f2","tid":1041460,"uid":45601,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180129/20288256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180129%2F20288256&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=e95e3bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180129%2F20288256&h=17fa513c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180129/20288256</a><br />\n清未民初都有喎，係咪矯枉過正呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T00:11:41.000Z","msg":"睇返頭兩個例子。<br />\n<br />\n「我的貨，賣是要賣，怕的是這客人有點欺人。我<span style=\"color: red;\">即便</span>肯賣與他，他未必真買。」<br />\n<br />\n「此女雖也膽大，一則從小便得高明傳授，人又靈慧機警，<span style=\"color: red;\">即便</span>有事，還可由她轉請乃師相助。」<br />\n<br />\n係，呢兩處「即使」「即便」互通，兩句情況下都啱用，但唔代表其他人用得啱。而且單靠兩句互通嘅情形去定奪兩個詞語嘅分別，係咪牽強左啲？有冇其他例子可以舉下？(真心想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c71bf869eb6f21ba621c8428aaff48e3017c4f","tid":1041460,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3547a5bcaa13598e4f40eb4b390397770c93d3a","tid":1041460,"uid":133877,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"睇返以前嘅漫畫,真係冇見過即便<br />\n奇就奇在得一兩個人咁寫就話姐,而家差唔多個個都寫即便<br />\n即係一班由以往譯/寫即使嘅都變埋做即便?<br />\n究竟係咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T00:14:51.000Z","msg":"其實真係近幾年先興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網絡發達，一個人用開好快就有大班人跟上去，連官方都唔例外&hellip;"},{"pid":"00a4148298ffbaa04ef9fe9f11d3286e2baa9b53","tid":1041460,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a1605d53659b6f46a271629c794b9e7637d37d","tid":1041460,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:48:41.000Z","msg":"台灣都係用即便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且用 弄不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T00:16:20.000Z","msg":"仲有拜託、拜「托」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家啲人寫少左字就越黎越多錯字"},{"pid":"bc75b78f0a42507f8a815509d66be9a74b5d5771","tid":1041460,"uid":23169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"我見「唔準」用得多過「唔准」添啦"},{"pid":"582a72b4cbdeb8dc37d27ec098a28f47bdf42881","tid":1041460,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc75b78f0a42507f8a815509d66be9a74b5d5771","tid":1041460,"uid":23169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"我見「唔準」用得多過「唔准」添啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T00:32:51.000Z","msg":"呢個真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5515af8a079c2942fbc489f7bdde63c01da0463a","tid":1041460,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"中文有樣野就係本來唔岩既用法<br />\n只要用既人夠多夠廣泛<br />\n就會收入字典 變成岩<br />\n有堅持既人唯有自己唔用"},{"pid":"05619afa7d8b96609133935193c7debf8d5345ac","tid":1041460,"uid":38623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5515af8a079c2942fbc489f7bdde63c01da0463a","tid":1041460,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"中文有樣野就係本來唔岩既用法<br />\n只要用既人夠多夠廣泛<br />\n就會收入字典 變成岩<br />\n有堅持既人唯有自己唔用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T01:39:08.000Z","msg":"啱呀，例如 啱字咁，個個都當岩係正字"},{"pid":"68a6f2837a8345d9832223ae26489a94fc7584e9","tid":1041460,"uid":76514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"麻木 盲目<br />\n帶帽 戴帽<br />\n大慨 大概<br />\n又係寫到錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc285f01dca6de385f8342a3eadb76095765f84f","tid":1041460,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"所以我一係寫即使 一係寫便是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72db9a5c2e8cf4e86094137255995b9af7332b61","tid":1041460,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"關於文字化繁為簡嘅演化：<br />\n<br />\n「可以猜得到，新語的特點會越來越明顯，包括的詞彙量越來越少、含義的限制越來越窄，一切將其作不適宜之用的可能性，越來越接近於零。一旦舊語被廢止，那麼通往歷史的最後之路，也將被徹底掐斷，歷史完全被重新改寫，假使有屢經搜查、劫後餘生的文獻儲存下來，散佈於世界的角落，估計也只有那些還懂得舊語的人才能讀懂。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;《1984》"}]}